{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "5078d241-15fa-4fc7-b988-090f40cb081c",
    "name": "Auth-Kit API Collection",
    "description": "## 🔐 Auth Kit API Collection — BuildBaseKit\n\nThis collection showcases a complete **JWT-based authentication and role-based authorization system** built with Spring Boot.\n\nDesigned for developers who want a **production-ready auth flow** without reinventing the wheel.\n\n---\n\n## ⚡ What’s Included\n\n- User Registration & Login\n    \n- Access & Refresh Token handling\n    \n- Token Refresh & Logout\n    \n- Protected endpoints\n    \n- Role-based access (User / Admin)\n    \n\n---\n\n## 🚀 Quick Flow\n\n1. Register → `/auth/register`\n    \n2. Login → `/auth/login` (tokens auto-saved)\n    \n3. Access protected routes using `access_token`\n    \n4. Refresh token → `/auth/refresh`\n    \n5. Logout → `/auth/logout`\n    \n\n---\n\n## 🔑 Setup\n\n- Set `base_url` → `http://localhost:8080`\n    \n- Tokens are automatically managed via scripts\n    \n\n---\n\n## 🌐 BuildBaseKit\n\nThis collection is part of **BuildBaseKit** — production-ready backend boilerplates.\n\n👉 [https://buildbasekit.com](https://buildbasekit.com/)\n\n---\n\nRun requests in sequence for best experience.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "_exporter_id": "47320634",
    "_collection_link": "https://go.postman.co/collection/47320634-5078d241-15fa-4fc7-b988-090f40cb081c?source=collection_link"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "AUTH",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Auth | Login [POST]",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const json = pm.response.json();\r",
                  "\r",
                  "// Set access token\r",
                  "if (json.accessToken) {\r",
                  "    pm.environment.set(\"access_token\", json.accessToken);\r",
                  "} else {\r",
                  "    console.error(\"No accessToken found in response\");\r",
                  "}\r",
                  "\r",
                  "// Set refresh token\r",
                  "if (json.refreshToken) {\r",
                  "    pm.environment.set(\"refresh_token\", json.refreshToken);\r",
                  "} else {\r",
                  "    console.error(\"No refreshToken found in response\");\r",
                  "}\r",
                  ""
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "packages": {}
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\r\n    \"username\":\"admin\",\r\n    \"password\":\"admin123\"\r\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/login",
              "host": [
                "{{base_url}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "auth",
                "login"
              ]
            }
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Auth | Refresh Token [POST]",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
